{
  "id": "RAW_7f959105",
  "title": "AI 时代，如何成为超级个体？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxNTAzNzU0Ng==&mid=2654901270&idx=2&sn=e9d7aa6ad66fcce243bd5231a4deb18d",
  "date": "2025-12-13 13:00:00",
  "author": "笔记侠",
  "siteName": "笔记侠",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: right;color: #0000007a;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px;widows: 1;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源</span></span></strong><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;| &nbsp;</span><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align: right;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;font-family:微软雅黑;widows:1;\"><span leaf=\"\">中信出版社&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;出版</span></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: right;color: #0000007a;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px;widows: 1;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 书籍《做有办法的人》 秘塔CEO 王一快</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-family:微软雅黑;widows:1;\"><span leaf=\"\">著</span></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: right;color: #0000007a;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px;widows: 1;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">责编</span></strong><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;| 柒 &nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">排版</span></strong><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;| 沐言</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: #0000007a;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px;widows: 1;text-align: right;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">第 9332</span></strong></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">篇深度好文：3852</span></strong></strong></strong></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">字 | 11 分钟阅读</span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">根据麦肯锡最新报告，受AIGC的影响最大的十大职业包括客户服务、行政助理、软件工程师等，这些职业面临着被自动化取代的风险。报告预测，在2030年至2060年间全球将会有50%的现有职业被取代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">至此，当我们看到AI直接对现实世界起了作用，再重新面对AI的快速迭代，很多人产生了这样的疑问：“AI会取代人类吗？当AI能完成大部分工作，那么人的价值又在哪里？”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">秘塔科技联合创始人王一快在《做有办法的人》中提出：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">“</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI不是取代，而是能力筛选器。</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">在不确定的时代里我们要审视自己的能力和AI能力重合的部分，特别是那些AI和我们做得一样好甚至更好的部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，从现在开始，准确地认知自己的工作要解决的问题，审视自己的工作内容，剔除其中重复性脑力劳动的部分，不断强化剩下的部分，才是真正的价值所在。”</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;width: 556.364px;background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, #a0a0a0, #fff7ea00) #ae515100;\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 5px 10px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一、</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration: none solid rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none solid rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI时代的个体成长，把自己作为方法</span></span></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个虚无主义盛行、AI 技术迅猛发展的时代，个人成长的空间似乎被压缩得越来越小。那么，在这样的大环境中，个体如何找到自己的出路？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">《做有办法的人》提出，首先需要的就是——</span></span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">重塑基本面系统</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">。基本面是一个人的综合竞争力，即综合运用自身各项基础能力解决复杂问题的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">根据在个人成长和职业发展中的不同作用和重要性，基本面系统可拆分为以下16项能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们想要在社会上立足，有所作为，靠的是向上的力。向上的力有很多，比如家庭背景、拥有的社会资源甚至运气。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这些都是无法人为决定的客观因素，唯有“基本面”是我们可以通过主观意志去改变和提升的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，如何重塑基本面，在人工智能的洪流中成为站在岸上的人？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.最简单的自我投资</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">体能即效率。保持运动的习惯，把自己的身体想象成银行，把运动当成存钱，一有空就存点儿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">人就是要在不缺钱的时候存钱，在身体健康的时候运动，在生活稳定的时候提升自己，在所有事情发生前掌握主动权，人生之路才会越走越顺。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">健康的体魄不仅带来充沛的精力，更能形成运动员人格，专注、坚韧、不受外界干扰，真正掌握身体和内心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">做个体面人，不止是外表体面，更是内在的修养。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100004262\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=30a40af6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib9ad17jOQMPgynDPyvkaa2eu5Dk0ptEqk61mDWPfaaCPXakUoocpcEzzpIL7E41Wk313w6NoyswVw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">与他人交往时，我们要记得不卑不亢，过度谄媚和刻意高冷都让人面目可憎。我们只需要带着善意和热情，正常与人沟通，自然会有良好的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">与同辈交流时，把他们当作朋友；对待长辈，则充分尊重。不要通过自我矮化来彰显对方高大，谦虚和自我矮化是两回事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">体面是我们在这个浮躁世界中展示自己的方式，也是改变我们生活的最直接、最有效的投资。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">扛住压力。打造坚强的内核，首先要提升自尊，成为一个有原则的、不被外部环境驱使的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">其次是要有向死而生的心态。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">把最差的结果想在前面，你会发现没有什么是你承受不了的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外还需要快速适应变化，保持持续进取的姿态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">适应力是衡量个人综合素质和能力的关键指标，它直接决定了你如何应对职场中的每一次转型、每一次挑战，能否在短时间内掌握新技能，能否适应更加灵活、复杂的工作模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">持续进取，需从两个方面入手：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">一是斗志：不论输赢，不计得失；</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">二是恒心：短期遵欲望，中期寻方向，长期追答案。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">不必到处问“我想要什么”，问题的答案不在别处，只能由你自己给出。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;width: 556.364px;background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, rgb(160, 160, 160), rgba(255, 247, 234, 0)) rgba(174, 81, 81, 0);\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 5px 10px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">二、</span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none solid rgb(176, 12, 3);font-size:17px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从“卷技能”到“卷认知”，实现个体不可替代性</span></span></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">著名作家尤瓦尔赫拉利曾多次提到:</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">人类社会正面临前所未有的变革。只适合技能的传授变得不再重要，一味接受、储存知识的大脑在今天一文不值，无论它有多年轻。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">《做有办法的人》一书则提出：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">超级个体的能力修炼，是要从被动接受到主动创造，把自己作为方法，打造职场的可替代性，最大化个人价值。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">个体只有完成从“手”到“脑”的跃迁，才能实现思维能力的突围。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.培养提出好问题的能力</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果AI已经可以解决人类的绝大多数问题，什么能力始终是我们的核心能力？答案是，</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">提出好问题的能力</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100004264\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=104935ad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib9ad17jOQMPgynDPyvkaa2e1hySRJszOkfLaBicySZjeffxIibYic8UTypsnHicbVetsKnwNmaJnHULtA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">所谓“好问题”，不是发散性的、不着边际的发问，好问题是带有明确目的性的精准的问题。遗憾的是，大多数人都不擅长问真实而具体的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，有与训练提问能力相匹配的手段吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段一：培养问题意识</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们要培养对矛盾的敏锐感知和认识，并主动寻求解决方法和途径。但看到并不等于认识，认识来自正确且有逻辑地归因，洞察原因才能提出好问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们看到了就业困难、降薪裁员的矛盾，那么原因是什么呢？如果归因于大环境差、国际局势不好、企业主吝啬且愚蠢，这就不是问题意识。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">问题意识是紧贴着“我”这个主体产生的：“我适不适合某个职业？”“我应该如何保持职场竞争力？”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">要习惯于用人性分析现象背后的道理，而不是习惯于“事情从来便如此”，这是培养提问能力的底层设定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段二：抛弃“我学的还不够”的想法</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们常认为自己学的知识还不够，还无法做某件事，这是一种懒惰而非谦虚的心态。单纯的知识积累并不等同于能力的提升，在低维度不断学习是无法实现突破的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要等待“学完”再行动，要给自己设定一个最小可行动计划，然后立即开始实践。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段三：先自己回答，再用AI验证</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">问出好问题的前提是，自己已经穷尽了思考和探索，这个过程是必不可少的，否则你的提问只是信息的索取，得到的答案也只会浮于表面，无法真正内化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100004274\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c2646def&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZYpa3icG6myjaWmcgX7hKENkLVia6f7PvIHEHFdpaiar0fRLxudsyEUlOYjW1aRuwvgnrpYs4cIAQkjMYics2ImLBw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%23imgIndex%3D11\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">“先培养问题意识”“抛弃学不够的焦虑”“先自己回答一遍”，这些不是技巧，而是在AI时代保持主体性的基本功。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">当AI成为每个人的“外脑”，真正拉开差距的不再是信息的占有，而是提问的质量：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">你问得越准，AI越强；你问得越深，成长越快。学会提问，就是学会在AI时代做自己的导师。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.培养灵活解决问题的能力—“创造力”</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人担心AI取代工作，但更本质的冲击是，AI正在重新定义“有价值的能力”。单纯输出创意，比创意多样性，此时此刻人已经不如AI了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，我们需要培养的是以高度机动性和灵活性解决问题的能力——创造力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段一：打破框架，寻找新方法</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">打破框架之前，要先了解框架。我们需要从那些在我们周围默默发生，但我们从未注意的事件中提炼出框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">先去解析一些普遍存在的问题，先做一个“知道分子”，就越了解真实事物的框架和边界</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">，接下来，就是用事实验证现有框架是否存在问题。这个过程就是打破框架，打破思维惯性，创造性地解决问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">创造力的养分，在于对世界保持开放与好奇的生命状态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100004269\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;text-align:center;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7352f2ec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib9ad17jOQMPgynDPyvkaa2ef9BxAuib7oA6XrQ325HeUIicBAco1O5qZsxic6a9PumKsmOfSO7JqoDIg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">这需要我们具备“空杯心态”，主动接触新框架、新语言，乐于探索和尝试。通过丰富的输入与深刻的反思，生发新的思维结构，为创造性突破积累素材。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段二：学会问“怎么能行”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">当遇到阻碍时，很多人的第一反应是追问“为什么会这样”“凭什么这样”，或者“这是谁的责任”。其实，我们最应该思考且只需要思考的是“怎么能行”，以及“有什么办法”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你第一时间想到的是“怎么能行”，就能主动去了解真实的规则，走上规则的链条，思考如何在框架外完成任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段三：把原创的想法落地</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">创造力是把原创的想法实际落地，它既要有创造的部分，又要有行动的部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">在面对复杂问题时，最有效的方式之一是迅速构建一个最小的、可行的解决方案，并通过实际应用获取反馈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">建立这个“最小遗憾模型”的过程不仅能加速学习，而且能以最低的成本迅速暴露潜在的问题，从而为后续调整和改进提供方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键在于不要把时间浪费在过度规划和追求完美上，而是要通过实际操作快速试错和优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.尊重规律，怀疑常识，培养正确的判断力</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">常识是要放在语境里、放在时间线上考虑的。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">常识是什么不重要，背后的规律才重要。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">遵循事物的基本规律，才能做正确的判断。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100004268\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71de6474&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib9ad17jOQMPgynDPyvkaa2eWd0go3weynbTbMNoHP9icVCL1BnZ0pYz5QHz5TiaLRDkrLumV2LiaUdGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D6\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">在培养判断力这件事上，建议大家先设定这样一个目标：1个月内，有意识地注意自己基于第一反应所做的判断。围绕这一目标，我们再来参考以下几个手段。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段一：</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">意识到自己的第一反应，但不轻易遵从。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段二：</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">把目标作为判断的出发点。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段三：</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">依照事实进行判断。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">手段四：</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">快速做判断，随时做调整。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.搭建AI知识库，构建“第二大脑”，培养资源整合的能力</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI知识库不同于传统的收藏夹，它是一个用AI对知识进行总结和分类的工具，建立在压缩和内化了绝大部分公共知识的大语言模型之上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，我们还可以将那些更具个人价值、无法从网络直接获取的信息存入其中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">当我们向AI知识库提问或提出需求时，它会结合你存入的个性化内容与模型自身的知识，提供精准回应。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI知识库能自动对信息进行存档，快速阅读并总结内容，帮助我们将大量的无序信息瞬间转化为有序的知识体系，大大减少记忆负担，像调取记忆一样快速找资料。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">《做有办法的人》要告诉大家的是：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">办法总比困难多，前提是，你已经开始把自己当成那个有办法的人来要求。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI时代，技术鸿沟在缩小，但心智鸿沟却在急剧拉大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">《做有办法的人》它给你的不是具体的AI工具教程，而是一套能让你在任何技术浪潮中都站稳脚跟的底层逻辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">毕竟，工具会迭代，但一个人解决问题的能力永远不会过时。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章根据《做有办法的人》一书核心观点，探讨了在 AI 时代个体如何通过重塑基本面能力和培养核心认知能力（提问、创造力、判断力）来提升个人价值，实现不可替代性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章根据《做有办法的人》一书核心观点，探讨了在 AI 时代个体如何通过重塑基本面能力和培养核心认知能力（提问、创造力、判断力）来提升个人价值，实现不可替代性。",
  "summary": "在 AI 快速发展、可能取代多项职业的背景下，文章提出 AI 并非取代人类，而是能力筛选器。作者引用《做有办法的人》的核心理念，强调个体应重塑基本面系统，包括提升体能、保持体面、扛住压力、适应变化和持续进取。此外，文章深入探讨了如何从“卷技能”转向“卷认知”，着重培养提出好问题、灵活解决问题（创造力）和正确的判断力，以及构建 AI 知识库来整合资源，从而在 AI 时代实现个人价值的最大化和不可替代性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 将成为能力筛选器，而非简单取代人类工作。",
      "explanation": "在 AI 时代，个体应审视自身能力与 AI 重合的部分，剔除重复性脑力劳动，强化不可替代的核心能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "重塑基本面系统是应对 AI 时代挑战的关键。",
      "explanation": "通过提升体能、保持体面、培养坚韧内核和持续进取精神，构建个人综合竞争力，掌握主动权。"
    },
    {
      "point": "从“卷技能”转向“卷认知”，培养高级思维能力。",
      "explanation": "核心能力应包括提出好问题的能力、灵活解决问题（创造力）和正确的判断力，以适应 AI 时代对人才的新要求。"
    },
    {
      "point": "学会提问是 AI 时代的核心竞争力，决定了与 AI 协作的效率与深度。",
      "explanation": "通过培养问题意识、敢于实践和先自我思考再借力 AI，提升提问质量，从而实现更深层次的成长。"
    },
    {
      "point": "培养创造力需打破思维框架、以“怎么能行”解决问题并落地原创思想。",
      "explanation": "通过开放心态、尝试新方法和最小可行性方案，将原创想法转化为实际行动，应对复杂挑战。"
    },
    {
      "point": "构建 AI 知识库，将碎片化信息整合为有序知识体系。",
      "explanation": "利用 AI 辅助管理个人与公共知识，减少记忆负担，提高信息检索效率和个性化知识应用能力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 不是取代，而是能力筛选器。",
    "从现在开始，准确地认知自己的工作要解决的问题，审视自己的工作内容，剔除其中重复性脑力劳动的部分，不断强化剩下的部分，才是真正的价值所在。",
    "当 AI 成为每个人的“外脑”，真正拉开差距的不再是信息的占有，而是提问的质量：你问得越准，AI 越强；你问得越深，成长越快。学会提问，就是学会在 AI 时代做自己的导师。",
    "创造力是把原创的想法实际落地，它既要有创造的部分，又要有行动的部分。",
    "办法总比困难多，前提是，你已经开始把自己当成那个有办法的人来要求。"
